or Zhaerze oilfield of SINOPEC-SONATRACH Joint Operation Consortium</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1429765047,1),('field:node:15','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:370:\"<p>\r\n54 pieces/sets of land oil and gas processing equipment of Peru PERENCO Company include: flares, metering skids, instrument air skids, various pump skids, hot oil heating skids, etc.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/peru/1-141119105R2Q5.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/peru/1-141119105UE61.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:355:\"<p>\n54 pieces/sets of land oil and gas processing equipment of Peru PERENCO Company include: flares, metering skids, instrument air skids, various pump skids, hot oil heating skids, etc.\n</p>\n<div class=\"country\">\n<div>\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/peru/1-141119105R2Q5.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/peru/1-141119105UE61.jpg\" /></div>\n</div>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1429329893,1),('field:node:16','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:771:\"<p>\r\nOur company provided combined heating separators and combined heating electric dehydrations to Ecuador National Andes Petroleum Company in 2007.  The oil and gas processing equipment is designed by us specially to meet the requirements of the development of oil and gas fields in South American tropical rain forest environment and is characterized by simplified process flow, high automation degree, high heating efficiency, good separation effect, etc. The product has entered Ecuador market, thus breaking up the monopoly by European and American countries in the region.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/ecuador/1-14111911054Y54.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/ecuador/1-1411191105316