re copyrights. Based on continuous technological innovations and preeminent R&D and design teams, HBP products and service are helping global oil-gas industry to provide highly efficient and environmental comprehensive solutions, currently its extensive applications spread over the lands of China, offshore oil-gas fields, and over 50 oil-gas fields among 30 oil producing countries. HBP has won attentions and approval from the society and customers for its equipment of high efficiency, energy-saving and environment protection as well as professional technical service, HBP has become a well-known enterprise for oil-gas field ground system, equipment and service.</p>\r\n<p>HBP has powerful machining and manufacturing capability, it has a production and research base for oil-gas field equipment in Daqing City, Heilongjiang Province, with coverage of 70,000 m2 and plant area of 40,000 m2; it also has massive scale and complete detecting equipment and manufacturing & machining equipment, with multiple laboratories and perfect quality control system.</p>\r\n<p>Standing on a starting line, HBP uses integration of upstream, middle and downstream as the blueprint to implement an international brand strategy via unremitting technological innovations, efficient service capacity, extensive involvement in international competition and active international market expansion; at the same time, through mergers and cooperation and so on approaches, the company tries to integrate upstream, middle and downstream resources and achieve the goal of becoming a comprehensive oil-gas field service supplier that has international influence. HBP will stick to the enterprise concepts of \"Continuous innovation, excelsior philosophy and harmonious development” to contribute to the society with the best products and service, and reward the customers and investors to create a beautiful and splendid tomorrow!</p>\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:13:\"filtered_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:3119:\"<p>China Oil HBP Group, founded in 1998, is an international supplier committed to providing comprehensive solutions for oil and gas development and exploitation, it is engaged in providing highly efficient and clean energies and energy production approaches for customers around the globe. Its main business scope is divided into three categories, equipment and project for oil and gas field, environment protection equipment and services for petro-chemicals as well as oil and gas development and exploitation.<br />\nHBP Group is headquartered in Peking, China, currently the corporation has 30 wholly-owned and holding subsidiaries, and 5 joint-stock companies, its subsidiaries and branch offices spread over in Middle East, Central Asia, and Africa and so on, with staff total of 1,300. On February 25th, 2011, HBP went listed on Shenzhen Stock Exchange with stock code 002554.<br />\nHBP has been insisting technological innovations and devoted to advanced technologies and products to create values for customers, it has established perfect R&amp;D organizational framework and powerful scientific research teams, currently it has over 50 inventions and patents of utility model as well as 40 software copyrights. Based on continuous technological innovations and preeminent R&amp;D and design teams, HBP products and service are helping global oil-gas industry to provide highly efficient and environmental comprehensive solutions, currently its extensive applications spread over the lands of China, offshore oil-gas fields, and over 50 oil-gas fields among 30 oil producing countries. HBP has won attentions and approval from the society and customers for its equipment of high efficiency, energy-saving and environment protection as well as professional technical service, HBP has become a well-known enterprise for oil-gas field ground system, equipment and service.<br />\nHBP has powerful machining and manufacturing capability, it has a production and research base for oil-gas field equipment in Daqing City, Heilongjiang Province, with coverage of 70,000 m2 and plant area of 40,000 m2; it also has massive scale and complete detecting equipment and manufacturing &amp; machining equipment, with multiple laboratories and perfect quality control system.<br />\nStanding on a starting line, HBP uses integration of upstream, middle and downstream as the blueprint to implement an international brand strategy via unremitting technological innovations, efficient service capacity, extensive involvement in international competition and active international market expansion; at the same time, through mergers and cooperation and so on approaches, the company tries to integrate upstream, middle and downstream resources and achieve the goal of becoming a comprehensive oil-gas field service supplier that has international influence. HBP will stick to the enterprise concepts of \"Continuous innovation, excelsior philosophy and harmonious development” to contribute to the society with the best products and service, and reward the customers and investors to create a beautiful and splendid tomorrow!</p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}}',0,1429753648,1),('field:node:3','a:1:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:10228:\"	<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/all/themes/venture_theme/css/style.css\"> <!-- Resource style -->\r\n	<script src=\"/sites/all/themes/venture_theme/js/modernizr.js\"></script> <!-- Modernizr -->\r\n<style>\r\n	.page-node #content-wrap img{\r\n		border:none;\r\n		margin:0px;\r\n		padding:0px;\r\n	}\r\n	.cd-timeline-img img{\r\n		top:30%;\r\n		left:30%;\r\n	}\r\n	#cd-timeline h2{\r\n		  color: #3d9991;\r\n		  font-family: \"HelveticaNeueW02-UltLtE 739241\";\r\n		  font-weight: bold;\r\n		  letter-spacing: 2px;\r\n		  font-size: 2em;\r\n	}\r\n	#cd-timeline span.cd-date{\r\n		  color: #3d9991;\r\n		  font-family: \"HelveticaNeueW02-UltLtE 739241\";\r\n		  font-weight: bold;\r\n		  letter-spacing: 2px;\r\n		  font-size: 1em;\r\n	}\r\n	#cd-timeline p{\r\n		  font-family: \"HelveticaNeueW02-ThinEx 739247\";\r\n		  line-height: 2em;\r\n		  font-weight: bold;\r\n		  letter-spacing: 2px;\r\n	\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<section id=\"cd-timeline\" class=\"cd-container\"><div class=\"cd-timeline-block\"><div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-picture\"><img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2014</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2014, HBP successfully purchased Kongnan Block of Dagang oil field 100% equities as a foreign country contractor, and its general operation scale was enlarged further; HBP contracted Iraq Missan Oil Field EPC project as the general contractor, which upgraded the company from traditional oil-gas field equipment business to EPC project general contracting.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2014</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2013</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2013, HBP extended its business to upstream oil and gas resources development realm, and successfully purchased fractional interests of production sharing contract of coal-seam gas exploitation of Shanxi Liulin The integration of upstream, middle and downstream has emerged.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2013</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2012</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2012, HBP established integrated development strategy of upstream and downstream, while stabilized oil-gas equipment and service business, HBP purchased Natural Gas Operation and Management Company and broke into area of downstream gas application business.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2012</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-location\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2010</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2010, HBP completed EP of Central Processing Station（CPF）of Iran MIS Oil Field and Iraq Ahdab Oil Field, and HBP technology and products gained footing in the middle east market.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2010</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-location\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2009</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2009, HBP vehicle-mounted mobile testing equipment won the bid among international famous enterprises, and its products made their way to Algeria, Kuwait and so on oversea market.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2009</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2008</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2008, HBP developed the first auto thermochemical and mechanical separation equipment for oily sludge in China, and made its first application in Daqing Oilfield, then subsequently developed mobile sludge treatment equipment, and environment protection engineering gradually became key part of HBP business development stra