t\" id=\"username\" name=\"username\" class=\"form-control\" placeholder=\"Name*\">\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"formdiv\">\r\n					<input type=\"text\" id=\"useremail\" name=\"useremail\" class=\"form-control\" placeholder=\"Email*\">\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"formdiv\">\r\n					<textarea id=\"userbody\" name=\"userbody\" class=\"form-control\" placeholder=\"Please input your content!\" style=\"height:100px;\"></textarea>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"formdiv\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<input type=\"button\" value=\"Contact Us\" class=\"form-btn\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;  padding: 10px 30px;\" onclick=\"contactusform();\">\r\n				</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\r\n	</form>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,8,8,'und',0,'<p>International Procurement Management</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Professional EPC procurement support team, with high-quality technical and professional talents</li>\r\n<li>Excellent international procurement website platform</li>\r\n<li>Focusing on needs of clients</li>\r\n<li>Well-established international supplier management system and procurement internal control system</li>\r\n<li>global procurement resources, processes, systems, market knowledge, and volume-leveraged pricing to maximize return on investment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Basing on domestic procurement advantages of the United States, HYPEC INC integrates superior petroleum equipment suppliers and global logistics resources, continuously supplies large machinery equipments, electrical instruments and automation products to our worldwide oil and gas customers for over 300 oil and gas fields, through strategic sourcing, material management, contract management, and logistics functions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>PART OF OUR SUPPLIERS</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"logo_div\">\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_881.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_883.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_885.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_887.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_889.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_891.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_893.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_896.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_898.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_900.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_902.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_904.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_906.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_908.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/procurement/procurement_910.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,9,9,'und',0,'<p>Our company has provided totally over 150 pieces (sets) of equipment including filter separators, cyclone separators, heating surface skids, production separator skids, metering separator skids, natural gas filters etc. to the oilfields of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd. including Zhanarol oilfield, Kenneyak suprasalt oilfield and sub-salt oilfield, North Buzachi oilfield, Ares oilfield, etc., China-Kazakhstan natural gas pipeline construction engineering and China-Kazakhstan Atasuisk-Alataw Pass crude oil pipeline construction engineering respectively. Our company undertook the EP task for 300*104 m3/d natural gas molecular sieve dehydration project of Zhanarol oilfield in 2008. After the project was put into production, the water dew point is controlled to be lower than -40℃, thus ensuring normal operation of nearly 400 gas injection wells. Our company undertook the EP task for the natural gas processing project of North Buzachi oilfield in 2011.</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/North Buzachi natural gas processing station project in Kazakhstan.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>North Buzachi natural gas processing station project in Kazakhstan</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/Zhanarol 4 gas lift and gas dehydration project in Kazakhstan.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Zhanarol 4# gas lift and gas dehydration project in Kazakhstan</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/The first international metering separator in Kazakhstan.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>The first international metering separator in Kazakhstan</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/North Buzachi desander.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>North Buzachi desander</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/Metering separator for sub-salt oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd..jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Metering separator for sub-salt oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd.</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/Metering separator for Zhanarol oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd..jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Metering separator for Zhanarol oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd.</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/Stages I and II testing separators for natural gas test production project in the south area of Zhanarol oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd..jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Stages I and II testing separators for natural gas test production project in the south area of Zhanarol oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd.</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/Indirect heating furnace for natural gas test production project in the south area of Zhanarol oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd..jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Indirect heating furnace for natural gas test production project in the south area of Zhanarol oilfield of Kazakhstan-CNPC AKTOBE Oil and Gas Co., Ltd.</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kazakhstan/North Buzachi heating separator project under construction (batches I and II) in 2014.png\" />\r\n		<h3>North Buzachi heating separator project under construction (batches I and II) in 2014</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,10,10,'und',0,'<p>\r\nOur company has successively provided 10 sets of separator skids and 3 sets of heating furnace skids for RONIER oilfield and BAOBAB oilfield in Chad since 2009. All of them have been well commissioned and put into production and are running normally.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/chad/Water jacket heater of BAOBAB oilfield in Chad.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Water jacket heater of BAOBAB oilfield in Chad </h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/chad/Primary production heating furnace of BAOBAB oilfield in Chad.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Primary production heating furnace of BAOBAB oilfield in Chad</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/chad/RONIER.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3></h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,13,13,'und',0,'<p>\r\nOur company began to enter the market in Kuwait in 2009 and has successively provided 10 sets of truck-mounted and skid-mounted testing separators and 1 set of sludge treatment unit for Kuwait Oil Company.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\nThe truck-mounted surface testing equipment (totally 2 sets) provided by us to Joint Operation Consortium of KGOC-Saudi Arabia Chevron Company in 2009</li>\r\n<li>\r\nThe skid-mounted surface testing equipment (totally 8 sets) provided by us to Joint Operation Consortium of KGOC-Saudi Arabia Chevron Company in 2009, 2011 and 2012</li>\r\n<li>\r\nThe oily sludge treatment equipment provided by us to Kuwait KOC in 2012</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kuwait/2009.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Truck-mounted surface testing equipment (totally 2 sets) provided by us to Joint Operation Consortium of KGOC-Saudi Arabia Chevron Company in 2009</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kuwait/2009-2011-2012.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>The skid-mounted surface testing equipment (totally 8 sets) provided by us to Joint Operation Consortium of KGOC-Saudi Arabia Chevron Company in 2009, 2011 and 2012</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/kuwait/2012.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>The oily sludge treatment equipment provided by us to Kuwait KOC in 2012</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,14,14,'und',0,'<p>\r\nOur company beat three France companies of strong strength in the competitive bidding and won the bid for the oil and gas processing equipment (including 8 production separator skids, 4 metering separator skids and 8 metering tank skids) for four metering oil transfer stations of Zhaerze oilfield in 2005. We won the bid for the project of Zhaerze oilfield again (including 6 horizontal three-phase separators, 3 vertical three-phase separators and 6 sets of vertical gas water two-phase separators) in 2007.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nOur company favorably completed the EP work for the oil transfer station of SBAA oilfield early in 2006 and provided the user with a complete set of equipment including production separator skids, metering separator skids, phase change heating furnace skids, transport pump skids and SCADA station control systems, all of which were favorably put into production in Sept. 2006.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nOur company won the bid for phase II engineering construction project of Zhaerze oilfield early in 2008 and designed and manufactured 6 production separators, 3 metering separators, 6 gas-water separators and 6 metering tanks to Zhaerze oilfield. We completed the manufacturing of the equipment highly efficiently at the end of 2008. After being put into production, the equipment runs well.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nAlgeria high pressure testing separator project includes totally two sets of truck-mounted vertical high pressure testing separators provided by us to Algeria ENSP Company. The designed pressure of the separator is 2175PSI. The separator was successfully put into production in 2011. Various indexes of the separator conform to the requirements of the design. The separator has been recognized and accepted by the Owner.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/algeria/ensp-2.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Truck-mounted surface testing equipment (2 sets) of Sonatrach ENSP</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/algeria/SONATRACH-5.jpg\" />\r\n		<h3>Free water separators (5 sets) for Zhaerze oilfield of SINOPEC-SONATRACH Joint Operation Consortium</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,15,15,'und',0,'<p>\r\n54 pieces/sets of land oil and gas processing equipment of Peru PERENCO Company include: flares, metering skids, instrument air skids, various pump skids, hot oil heating skids, etc.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/peru/1-141119105R2Q5.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/peru/1-141119105UE61.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,16,16,'und',0,'<p>\r\nOur company provided combined heating separators and combined heating electric dehydrations to Ecuador National Andes Petroleum Company in 2007.  The oil and gas processing equipment is designed by us specially to meet the requirements of the development of oil and gas fields in South American tropical rain forest environment and is characterized by simplified process flow, high automation degree, high heating efficiency, good separation effect, etc. The product has entered Ecuador market, thus breaking up the monopoly by European and American countries in the region.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/ecuador/1-14111911054Y54.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/ecuador/1-141119110531646.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,17,17,'und',0,'<p>\r\nCyclone separator and filter separator for Turkmenistan Bagtyyarlyk natural gas gathering and transportation project\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/turkmenistan/turkmenistan.jpg\" />\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,18,18,'und',0,'<div class=\"country\">\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/uzbekistan/Cyclone separator and filter separator of PetroChina Uzbekistan Company.jpg\" />\r\n                <h3>Cyclone separator and filter separator of PetroChina Uzbekistan Company</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<img src=\"/imgs/country/uzbekistan/Uzbekistan flare project.jpg\" />\r\n                <h3>Uzbekistan flare project</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html');
