INSERT INTO `field_revision_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,1,1,'und',0,'<div  class=\"profile\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">HYPEC INC</span> is an international trading and technical service company for oil gas EPC project business, with unlimited potential and abundant resources support.  The Group Company is committed to providing comprehensive solutions for oil gas development and exploitation, and it is engaged in providing highly efficient and clean energies and energy production approaches for customers across the globe. Its main business scope is divided into three categories, oil gas equipments and projects, petrochemical and environment protection equipments and services, as well as oil gas development and exploitation.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">\r\nOur products and services provide highly efficient, environment friendly and comprehensive solutions to global oil gas industry, currently covering the onshore and offshore oil & gas fields in China, and extensively applied over 50 oil gas fields among 30 oil producing countries. Nowadays Group Company have more than 30 branch companies and offices operating in USA, Middle East, Central Asia, Africa and so on.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"\">\r\nThe headquarter located in China has powerful processing and manufacturing capability, with 70,000 m2 sized production and research base and 40,000 m2 sized plant for oil gas equipment in Daqing City, Heilongjiang Province. It also has processing, manufacturing and detecting equipments of massive scale and complete functions, with multiple laboratories and perfect quality control systems.\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>PART OF OUR BUSINESS PARTNERS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"logo_div\">\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1458.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1460.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1462.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1464.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1466.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1468.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1470.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1472.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1474.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1476.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1478.png\" /></div>\r\n	<div><img src=\"/imgs/ourclient/hypec-1455.png\" /></div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,2,2,'und',0,'<p>China Oil HBP Group, founded in 1998, is an international supplier committed to providing comprehensive solutions for oil and gas development and exploitation, it is engaged in providing highly efficient and clean energies and energy production approaches for customers around the globe. Its main business scope is divided into three categories, equipment and project for oil and gas field, environment protection equipment and services for petro-chemicals as well as oil and gas development and exploitation.</p>\r\n<p>HBP Group is headquartered in Peking, China, currently the corporation has 30 wholly-owned and holding subsidiaries, and 5 joint-stock companies, its subsidiaries and branch offices spread over in Middle East, Central Asia, and Africa and so on, with staff total of 1,300. On February 25th, 2011, HBP went listed on Shenzhen Stock Exchange with stock code 002554.</p>\r\n<p>HBP has been insisting technological innovations and devoted to advanced technologies and products to create values for customers, it has established perfect R&D organizational framework and powerful scientific research teams, currently it has over 50 inventions and patents of utility model as well as 40 software copyrights. Based on continuous technological innovations and preeminent R&D and design teams, HBP products and service are helping global oil-gas industry to provide highly efficient and environmental comprehensive solutions, currently its extensive applications spread over the lands of China, offshore oil-gas fields, and over 50 oil-gas fields among 30 oil producing countries. HBP has won attentions and approval from the society and customers for its equipment of high efficiency, energy-saving and environment protection as well as professional technical service, HBP has become a well-known enterprise for oil-gas field ground system, equipment and service.</p>\r\n<p>HBP has powerful machining and manufacturing capability, it has a production and research base for oil-gas field equipment in Daqing City, Heilongjiang Province, with coverage of 70,000 m2 and plant area of 40,000 m2; it also has massive scale and complete detecting equipment and manufacturing & machining equipment, with multiple laboratories and perfect quality control system.</p>\r\n<p>Standing on a starting line, HBP uses integration of upstream, middle and downstream as the blueprint to implement an international brand strategy via unremitting technological innovations, efficient service capacity, extensive involvement in international competition and active international market expansion; at the same time, through mergers and cooperation and so on approaches, the company tries to integrate upstream, middle and downstream resources and achieve the goal of becoming a comprehensive oil-gas field service supplier that has international influence. HBP will stick to the enterprise concepts of \"Continuous innovation, excelsior philosophy and harmonious development” to contribute to the society with the best products and service, and reward the customers and investors to create a beautiful and splendid tomorrow!</p>','','filtered_html'),('node','page',0,3,3,'und',0,'	<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/all/themes/venture_theme/css/style.css\"> <!-- Resource style -->\r\n	<script src=\"/sites/all/themes/venture_theme/js/modernizr.js\"></script> <!-- Modernizr -->\r\n<style>\r\n	.page-node #content-wrap img{\r\n		border:none;\r\n		margin:0px;\r\n		padding:0px;\r\n	}\r\n	.cd-timeline-img img{\r\n		top:30%;\r\n		left:30%;\r\n	}\r\n	#cd-timeline h2{\r\n		  color: #3d9991;\r\n		  font-family: \"HelveticaNeueW02-UltLtE 739241\";\r\n		  font-weight: bold;\r\n		  letter-spacing: 2px;\r\n		  font-size: 2em;\r\n	}\r\n	#cd-timeline span.cd-date{\r\n		  color: #3d9991;\r\n		  font-family: \"HelveticaNeueW02-UltLtE 739241\";\r\n		  font-weight: bold;\r\n		  letter-spacing: 2px;\r\n		  font-size: 1em;\r\n	}\r\n	#cd-timeline p{\r\n		  font-family: \"HelveticaNeueW02-ThinEx 739247\";\r\n		  line-height: 2em;\r\n		  font-weight: bold;\r\n		  letter-spacing: 2px;\r\n	\r\n	}\r\n</style>\r\n<section id=\"cd-timeline\" class=\"cd-container\"><div class=\"cd-timeline-block\"><div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-picture\"><img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2014</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2014, HBP successfully purchased Kongnan Block of Dagang oil field 100% equities as a foreign country contractor, and its general operation scale was enlarged further; HBP contracted Iraq Missan Oil Field EPC project as the general contractor, which upgraded the company from traditional oil-gas field equipment business to EPC project general contracting.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2014</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2013</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2013, HBP extended its business to upstream oil and gas resources development realm, and successfully purchased fractional interests of production sharing contract of coal-seam gas exploitation of Shanxi Liulin The integration of upstream, middle and downstream has emerged.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2013</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-picture\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2012</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2012, HBP established integrated development strategy of upstream and downstream, while stabilized oil-gas equipment and service business, HBP purchased Natural Gas Operation and Management Company and broke into area of downstream gas application business.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2012</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-location\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2010</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2010, HBP completed EP of Central Processing Station（CPF）of Iran MIS Oil Field and Iraq Ahdab Oil Field, and HBP technology and products gained footing in the middle east market.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2010</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-location\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2009</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2009, HBP vehicle-mounted mobile testing equipment won the bid among international famous enterprises, and its products made their way to Algeria, Kuwait and so on oversea market.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2009</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2008</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2008, HBP developed the first auto thermochemical and mechanical separation equipment for oily sludge in China, and made its first application in Daqing Oilfield, then subsequently developed mobile sludge treatment equipment, and environment protection engineering gradually became key part of HBP business development strategy.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2008</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2007</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2007, HBP developed oil tank auto-mechanical cleaning equipment that for the first time China has its own intellectual property right, which changed the imported situation.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2007</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2006</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2006, HBP contracted gas-lift processing project in Zhalaroer of Kazakstan, and extended HBP oil gas comprehensive processing technology industry.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2006</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2005</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2005, HBP contracted the EP work of Central Processing Station (CPF) of Syria GBB Oil Field; HBP has made its great strike in international oil-gas processing market.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2005</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2004</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2004, HBP developed high pressure and high temperature testing equipment of international advanced standard, which it broke the European and American monopoly in this area, HBP oil-gas mining equipment had made a great break-through.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2004</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2003</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2003, HBP oil-gas processing equipment broke into marine oil market, it provided set equipment for ocean platform, FPSO and land terminals subsequently.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2003</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2002</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2002, HBP targeted automation control area, by combining its technological and talent advantages, it formulated a diversified path of development that is practical.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2002</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2001</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2001, the company invented high efficiency oil-gas-water-sand four-phase separator, which successfully solved the difficult issue of separation of heavy extra-high water-cut produced fluid, and this defined the leading advantage of HBP in high efficiency separation area in China.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2001</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>2000</h2>\r\n				<p>In 2000, HBP accurately located its strategy during the embryo, and focused on oil-gas treating process area, and to create more space for company expansion via expansion and innovations.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">2000</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>1999</h2>\r\n				<p>In 1999, HBP had developed the low shear cone valve type polymer flow regulator for tertiary oil extraction of international standard, which helped Daqing Oilfield to achieve “One pump versus multiple wells \" of tertiary oil extraction process revolution, and HBP made his sail successfully.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">1999</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"cd-timeline-block\">\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-img cd-movie\">\r\n				<img src=\"img/cd-icon-movie.svg\" alt=\"Movie\">\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-img -->\r\n			<div class=\"cd-timeline-content\">\r\n				<h2>1998</h2>\r\n				<p>In 1998, Beijing China Oil HBP Science and Technology Company Limited was initiated and registered by Huang Song, Bai Minggen, Pan Feng.</p>\r\n				<span class=\"cd-date\">1998</span>\r\n			</div> <!-- cd-timeline-content -->\r\n		</div> <!-- cd-timeline-block -->\r\n		\r\n	</section> <!-- cd-timeline -->\r\n\r\n<script src=\"/sites/all/themes/venture_theme/js/main.js\"></script> <!-- Resource jQuery -->\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,4,4,'und',0,'<div class=\"page_img\">\r\n	<img src=\"/imgs/bg3.jpg\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Grow with energy development; make the energy cleaner and the life better.</p>\r\n<p>Humankind is great because we have dreams, an enterprise prospers because it has its culture，HBP corporate culture derives from its accumulation, cohesion and sedimentation process during its long-term enterprise development, the enterprise has been growing since it came into being, its corporate culture shows HBP man\'s spirit during the development.</p>\r\n<p>Corporate vision: Grow with energy development; make the energy cleaner and the life better</p>\r\n<p>Corporate mission: enhance organizing capacity continuously and keep adding more values to the customers</p>\r\n<p>Core values: innovate via science and technology, with human as the base and customer in the center, guided by the market</p>\r\n<p>Development goals: Strive to be first class international supplier for oil gas service</p>\r\n<p>Corporate merits: Honest and true to reality, incorruption and outspokenness, as good as our word</p>\r\n<p>Team cooperation: open-minded, positive and optimistic, mutual help and learning, to create simple, trusted and pleasant team, to create a team culture guided with performance</p>\r\n','','full_html'),('node','page',0,5,5,'und',0,'<div class=\"pageheaderimg5\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>We have Grade II qualification certificate for oil field surface construction project in the oil and gas industry (including off-shore oil), Class I, II III Grade A1 A2 pressure vessel design and manufacture certificate issued by National Quality Inspection General Bureau, pressure pipe design certificate of Grade GC1, GC2 GC3, Level C boiler manufacture certificate, U, U2 S steel seal certificate for pressure vessel manufacture issued by American Society of Mechanical Engineers (ASME), R certificate issued by NBBI-The National Board of Boiler and Pressure Vessel Inspectors, API Spec 12J API Spec 12K product logo certificate issued by American Petroleum Institute, and has passed the quality management system certification ISO9001, the environmental management system certification ISO14001, occupational health and safety certification OHSMS18001 and the quality management system certification API Q1.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','','full_html'),('node','page',0,6,6,'und',0,'<style>\r\n\r\n	.page-node #content-wrap .container li img{\r\n		border:none;\r\n		padding:0px;\r\n		margin:0px;\r\n	}\r\n	.grid li{\r\n		list-style:none;\r\n		width:30%;\r\n		margin-left:3%;\r\n		float:left;\r\n		margin-bottom:50px;\r\n	}\r\n	.grid li figure{\r\n		background:#fff;\r\n		-moz-border-radius: 30px;\r\n		-webkit-border-radius: 30px;\r\n		border-radius: 30px;\r\n		text-align:center;\r\n		border:3px solid #f1f1f1;\r\n	}\r\n	\r\n	.grid figcaption {\r\n		-moz-border-radius-bottomleft: 30px;\r\n		-webkit-border-bottom-left-radius: 30px;\r\n		border-bottom-left-radius: 30px;\r\n		-moz-border-radius-bottomright: 30px;\r\n		-webkit-border-bottom-right-radius: 30px;\r\n		border-bottom-right-radius: 30px;\r\n		padding:2px;\r\n		background:#f1f1f1;\r\n		margin-bottom:-30px;\r\n	}\r\n	.grid figcaption a{\r\n		  padding: 5px 15px;\r\n		border-radius: 2px;\r\n		 display: inline-block;\r\n	}\r\n	.grid figcaption p{\r\n		margin-top:15px;\r\n                text-align:center;\r\n	}\r\n	.grid figcaption h3{\r\n		margin-top:15px;\r\n	}\r\n	\r\n	.grid li figure:hove